Wildflower Finder

What's that flower?

Just upload a picture of a flower and let Wildflower Finder's model tell you what it is.

Accurate

Wildflower Finder is 97% accurate for 13 species of Colorado wildflowers.

Easy to Use

Just upload an image of a flower from your phone or desktop.

Responsive

In today's world where devices come in every shape and size, Vitality will responsively adapt to look great on any screen!

Built with Love

All themes by Start Bootstrap are crafted with care. Thank you for choosing Vitality and being a customer!

Supported Species

Flower species currently included in the app

Achillea lanulosa Common Yarrow
Adenolinum lewisii Blue Flax
Alyssum simplex (Alyssum parviflorum) Wild Alyssum
Arnica cordifolia Heartleaf Arnica
Cerastium arvense Field Chickweed
Delphinium Nuttallianum Larkspur

Mertensia lanceolata Foothills Mertensia
Padus virginiana Chokecherry
Penstemon virens Bluemist Penstemon
Phlox longifolia Long-leaf Phlox
Senecio integerrimus Lamb's Tongue Ragwort
